frus:attachment.p:
—provide a concrete manifestation of the flexibility in our approach
                                and perhaps a stimulus for some real give-and-take when negotiations
                                resume in Geneva;

—serve the tactical objective of having fleshed-out US positions on
                                the table to counter the Soviet moratoria and “space-strike” arms
                                ban proposals and to shift the public away from SDI to our arms control agenda;
